1 pay the property owner's entire balance under this subsection
2 unless at the same time the property owner pays all interest
3 due at the next interest paying period.
4 (b) If a person who exercises the right to prepay the person's
5 assessment fully pays the assessment and interest, all interest and
6 liability as to the assessed property ceases.
